00:34:05,349 --> 00:34:06,850
Meu Deus!

449
00:34:14,693 --> 00:34:16,151
Vai, vai, vai!

450
00:34:18,195 --> 00:34:19,494
Jesus!

451
00:34:23,283 --> 00:34:24,583
Merda!

452
00:34:35,546 --> 00:34:37,339
Minhas pernas!

453
00:34:45,556 --> 00:34:47,973
